2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a cellular network and the use of multiple base stations for macrodiversity, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions the use of millimeter wave frequencies, which are commonly used in multimedia applications. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the impact of blockages on system reliability, which is a topic in systems and control. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) - The paper analyzes the performance of the cellular network with random blockages and considers the impact of various factors on system reliability, which falls under the domain of performance analysis.
